The Bridges of Madison County;;87;;90;;PG-13;;A moving love story about a photographer on assignment to shoot the historic bridges of Madison County. He meets a housewife, whose husband and children are away on a trip, and the film traces a brief affair that is never sordid but instead one of two soul mates who have met too late.;;Romance,Drama;;Clint Eastwood;;1995;;Clint Eastwood,Meryl Streep,Annie Corley,Victor Slezak,Jim Haynie,Sarah Kathryn Schmitt,Christopher Kroon,Phyllis Lyons,Debra Monk,Richard Lage,Michelle Benes,Alison Wiegert,Brandon Bobst,Pearl Faessler,R.E. Faessler,Tania Mishler,Billie McNabb,Art Breese,Lana Schwab,Larry Loury;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bridges_of_madison_county